    "html": "<div\n        style=\"width: 351px; height: 114px; flex: none; position: absolute; left: 3.2%; right: 3.2%; top: 5.97%; bottom: 90.07%; z-index: 17\">\n        <div\n          style=\"width: 351px; height: 114px; flex: none; position: absolute; left: 0%; right: 0%; top: 0%; bottom: 0%; z-index: 0\">\n          <div\n            style=\"width: 351px; height: 114px; flex: none; position: absolute; left: 0%; right: 0%; top: 0%; bottom: 0%; z-index: 0\">\n            <div style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; z-index: 0\">\n              <img src=\"./asset/icons/svg_a1293347.svg\" />\n            </div>\n            <p\n              style=\"width: 325px; color: #45536B; font-size: 11.5px; font-family: FZLTHJW--GB1; text-align: justify; line-height: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.2px; position: absolute; left: calc(100% - 351px + 12px); top: calc(100% - 114px + 41px); z-index: 1\">\n              SEMI报告显示，2026年Q1全球半导体设备销售额达365.5亿美元，同比增长14%，创单季历史新高。AI相关投资持续驱动先进逻辑、DRAM及先进封装产能扩张，半导体景气上行，产业链相关环节或迎布局机遇。\n            </p>\n            <p\n              style=\"color: #A1A9B3; font-size: 9px; font-family: FZLTHJW--GB1; text-align: justify; line-height: 9px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; position: absolute; left: calc(100% - 351px + 135px); top: calc(100% - 114px + 94px); z-index: 2\">\n              资料来源：财联社，发布于2026.06.14\n            </p>\n            <p\n              style=\"color: #2E3D65; font-size: 13.5px; font-family: MiSans; text-align: justify; font-weight: 600; line-height: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; position: absolute; left: calc(100% - 351px + 103px); top: calc(100% - 114px + 15px); z-index: 3\">\n              365亿美元！半导体设备销售创新高\n            </p>\n            <div\n              style=\"position: absolute; left: 2.56%; right: 72.65%; top: 8.77%; bottom: 71.05%; z-index: 4\">\n              <img src=\"./asset/icons/svg_ee3f257e.svg\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <img\n            src=\"./asset/images/6eb5228a1001f3f9c31dee65e937